Package: pico-ctl
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-serial, ${misc:Depends}
Description: All-in-one CLI for managing a Raspberry Pi Pico over USB serial
 Upload files, backup, monitor, reset, and inspect a Raspberry Pi Pico
 running MicroPython — all from a single pico_ctl command.
